name: The Forest of Enlightenment
description:
Close to New Year, I stumbled upon an urban forest of the metaphysical, a concept in my own mind, which on submitting to it, would grant wishes beyond comprehension. The metaphysical and meta verse is synonymous, and therefore a figment of this imagination exists on the tezos block-chain.

Or just use it as a cool wallpaper for your desktop, or print out a physical copy for your bedroom!

1920x1080PX of only 10 unique copies.
